<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>7 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS FULLER SERIES - INSTALL - GEAR SHIFT LEVER HOUSING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="2">
        <title>GEAR SHIFT LEVER HOUSING</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Check the shifter housing assembly to make sure the shift block notches are in the neutral
                position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13025j7">inset, Figure 197</hotlnk>). Install the gear shift lever housing on the
                shifter housing, fitting the lever tip into the shift block notches.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13025j7" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13025j7" filename="../figg13/G13025j7.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 197. Make Sure Shift Block Notches are in Neutral Position and Install Gear Shift Lever
                Housing
            </caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install retaining bolts in the housing flange (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13025j8">Figure 198</hotlnk>). Tighten to 35 to 45 ft-lbs. (47 to 61 N&#183; m).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13025j8" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13025j8" filename="../figg13/G13025j8.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 198. Install Retaining Bolts in Housing Flange</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
